    answer: "Most bowing wall repairs are completed within 2-5 days. Carbon fiber reinforcement takes 1-2 days, while wall anchor installation or partial rebuilding may take 3-5 days. Timeline depends on wall condition, access, and weather for exterior work."
  },
  {
